==Summary==
Players can mix and match all the skills in the game to make almost any kind of character they can think of. Our active development means some of the Templates below might be out of date, so it is always best to check the Forums, Discord, or Test Shard for current stats. Below are some Templates crafted by the community sorted by Archetypes.

