<p style="color: red"><strong>Warning: We strongly recommend creating all of your PvM characters on the same account!</strong></p>
<p>This is because [[Mastery Chain]] experience (the main long term progression system on Outlands) is account bound and spreading it out over multiple accounts will slow down your progression significantly.</p>

